Introduction

Nayoung is a South Korean singer and dancer under Cube Entertainment. She is a member of the girl group LIGHTSUM and a former member of the disbanded trainee group Banana Culture Newkid.

In 2018, as a trainee, Nayoung participated in Mnet's survival show "Produce 48" and she was eliminated in the eleventh episode after achieving 21st place.

Nayoung debuted as a member of the girl group LIGHTSUM on June 10, 2021, with their first single "Vanilla".
